data.description: Sellers love it but must move back!  3 bedrooms down with split floor plan.  Large kitchen, formal dining room and laundry.  Upstairs is bedroom 4 and bonus/play area.  Walk-in attic space or could be finished out for bedroom, bonus or media room.  Home has a lot to offer and just under half acre lot.  Atoka is the place to be with a small town feel and just minutes to Memphis!
